NUMBER 481
NAME Eye of the Storm
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
You are a mile above the ground in the center of a raging storm. Far below your feet, you can see the geometric patterns of a few plowed fields surrounded by a dark green forest.
The storm blows fiercely all around you and bolts of lightning arc across the sky.
*DESCRIPTION_END
